  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Relationship between human microbiota and epidemiology of lung cancer
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this study,We aim to find some kinds of human microbiota , which were associated with
      development of non-small cell lung cancer.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
